Source: Dominion
Author:
Vol / Page: C7
Edition:
Quote: Cow condition is no longer a concern under his once-a-day milking regime. When we went to once-a-day milking they very quickly picked up condition.
Notes:

Date: 20/9/2002
Source: Taranaki Daily News
Author:
Vol / Page: Farming Supplement 5
Edition:
Quote: Mrs Tong said that because the once-a-day approach required a slightly bigger herd, it did take longer to milk ...Our once-a-day cows were at least half a condition score above the twice-a-day cows throughout the year, so they are heavier. [once-a-day]
